    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Rep. Kevin Kiley and I speak on all things politics! Join the conversation by calling in before 8PM and giving us your take! \n\n\u260e\ufe0f Call: 866-967-6887",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034411174754656423",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-18T23:26:36+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "\ud83d\udea8 TONIGHT: The country is moving FAST and I need YOUR voice on this:\n\n- The SAVE Act...\n- Oil prices going UP...\n\nAnd somehow we\u2019re supposed to believe everything is under control?!\n\nI don\u2019t think so.\n\n\ud83d\udcde CALL IN: 866-967-6887\n\nLet\u2019s talk about it LIVE on Straight Shooter @SIRIUSXM!",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034389485429866650",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-18T22:00:25+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "We are in the SECOND HALF \u2026trust me, we are just getting warmed up! \n\nCALL THE SHOW: 888-623-3646\nLISTEN NOW: sxm.app.link/MadDogRadio",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034331930469212284",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-18T18:11:42+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "You know what time it is!!! Call in today from 1pm - 3pm EST!!! Don\u2019t sit on your take, SAY IT!",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034315342986494361",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-18T17:05:48+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "The SAVE Act is sparking major debate across the country!\nIs this about protecting election integrity\u2026 or restricting voter access? \n\nHere's a way to get your voice heard: Record or text your political take for my Straight Shooter Show every Wednesday at 6pm -8pm EST! bit.ly/4sSoDQ4\n\nVideo",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034299073293946966",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-18T16:01:09+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
    },
    {
      "voiceId": "stephen-a-smith",
      "voiceName": "Stephen A. Smith",
      "platform": "x",
      "text": "Make sure you tune this morning! We are LIVE!",
      "sourceUrl": "https://x.com/stephenasmith/status/2034286252443197482",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-18T15:10:12+00:00",
      "type": "tweet"
